"""
Bubble Editor CLI - Scalable command-line tool for Bubble element manipulation.

Usage:
    python bubble_cli.py update-text <reusable> <search-text> <new-text>
    python bubble_cli.py update-name <reusable> <element-name> <new-name>
    python bubble_cli.py update-placeholder <reusable> <element-name> <new-placeholder>

Examples:
    python bubble_cli.py update-text missions "Gerencie as missões" "Novo texto"
    python bubble_cli.py update-name gp-numero "in phone" "in whatsapp"
    python bubble_cli.py update-placeholder gp-numero "in phone" "+55 11 99876-5432"
"""

